Config.name: shabeer
Config.introduction: Hi, I'm Shabeer, a passionate Flutter App Developer from India with hands-on experience in designing and developing mobile applications. I specialize in Dart, Python, Firebase, and Django, with expertise in UI/UX design, state management, and API integration. I thrive in collaborative environments and enjoy solving complex problems efficiently to deliver impactful applications.Recently, I worked as a Mobile App Developer Intern at 8Queens Technology, where I developed a feature-rich chat application that improved user engagement by 25%. I'm always eager to apply my skills and creativity to create dynamic and user-friendly applications.
